" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身企成日 又搬啲碗碟已經攰 仲要加重嗰膝頭嘅負荷<br />\n點解仲要人跪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebeac5ac4e1031b1b3701a3145ca7dd8c74c05af","tid":434902,"uid":127223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T03:29:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個海鮮火鍋好食 但好貴 又慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 次次最少等成廿分鐘</blockquote><br />\n講真真係好睇嗰廚房做野快唔快手<br />\n如果執火鍋嗰位快嘅 出餸嗰位唔冧檔 可以快快手出 樓面同事又醒水俾定嗰爐 咁都唔係等好耐嘅"},{"pid":"86f3862112b4440633318fdb51fe2ae10fe96248","tid":434902,"uid":53173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T03:30:28.000Z","msg":"啲鍋既雞湯點整出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9814ab2117171406f427215367fe92376d1f285","tid":434902,"uid":127223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T05:57:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲鍋既雞湯點整出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁多嗰鍋 我剩係食過牛鍋咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想食海鮮鍋啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5a56a1b405dc78293f6cb73658c56cffae41e6","tid":434902,"uid":41052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T06:55:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲客麻唔麻煩？</blockquote><br />\n閪到飛起<br />\n有啲客一入黎就已經西口西面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed0036cdb738bfd51ba60ce03db19125903d36e","tid":434902,"uid":41052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T09:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6801fcbb82e5e7403ea4214557ec453ece736e6c","tid":434902,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB