\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794081f33da9c8fe3d3cdde854c8c3ea945dabc7","tid":434902,"uid":127223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:37:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個燒魷魚勁好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f5b6852cf31e867d05c4f152dee6a0918a1d7dd","tid":434902,"uid":124058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T13:52:21.000Z","msg":"係咪無左章魚餅啦？<br />\n同埋個牛油帶子點整 好好食"},{"pid":"b9b1531e33cec2eaa9da1fd6c3b99ee8a29bbe03","tid":434902,"uid":2860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T14:26:21.000Z","msg":"中意食佢既石鍋飯同雞軟骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b51c1de271eeaf67ee92f945191558ce3aa2e8","tid":434902,"uid":68389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T14:55:10.000Z","msg":"芝士年糕幾時冇左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"4faf56dc0a55f59126ffefe3c4dcdd733ab147ba","tid":434902,"uid":146773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T14:57:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主翻邊間？"},{"pid":"2caf1f031bd7467ff9a939afc0a3bf46ed982e2e","tid":434902,"uid":146869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T15:32:57.000Z","msg":"揀咗員工888未阿？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad8a69661f8c031e10498dadd65867f103700c8a","tid":434902,"uid":98167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T15:42:53.000Z","msg":"前pt留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26998c3bcc2fe9314914f04749639188ce26324","tid":434902,"uid":41052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:25:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主翻邊間？</blockquote><br />\n油尖旺嗰頭"},{"pid":"f17f47821d6b448032504dc8892a99aabb2e4da1","tid":434902,"uid":6329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:36:41.000Z","msg":"點解愈來愈難食？<br />\n以前有定期食，但後期難食到仆街，仲要食左幾百蚊一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n轉左食其他野好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24dc1ffef6abeb37624186de1ec67baf6eaeee74","tid":434902,"uid":127223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:38:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嚮和民既早餐最抵食係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我嗰間冇早餐架 得lunch 同set<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9dc4ed1eed37cd67397ae3431ccda06de90aa1","tid":434902,"uid":127223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:47:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪無左章魚餅啦？<br />\n同埋個牛油帶子點整 好好食</blockquote><br />\n章魚餅應該冇咗啦 早排轉menu<br />\n我好多嘢都冇食過 牛油帶子都係其中一樣<br />\n想知係咩味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋牛油帶子係其中一樣野成日冇貨"},{"pid":"6449a1ec21a5f3aeec2f3a9dd7da353c7976f910","tid":434902,"uid":127223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:50:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>芝士年糕幾時冇左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n應該就係半個月前轉menu嘅時候冇咗<br />\n個個客都問係咪轉老細所以轉menu<br />\n我真係唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我只係一個小薯仔咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb3032b78dcb1f61611cd4c3aed15e061644dd4","tid":434902,"uid":127223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T16:54:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揀咗員工888未阿？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n揀黎揀去都係嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經諗唔到食乜好"},{"pid":"0381f044d592990086ff4d5cb3a00579ae1995f2","tid":434902,"uid":127223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T17:11:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解愈來愈難食？<br />\n以前有定期食，但後期難食到仆街，仲要食左幾百蚊一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n轉左食其他野好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實每間餐飲都會遇到啲咁嘅情況<br />\n應該就係睇嗰日邊個返廚房嗰啲位<br />\n如果係熟手嘅 野食一定有返啲水平<br />\n但咁啱嘅新手 或者平時做野拿西啲嘅就會差啲"},{"pid":"074fc55f487e00bbee0f3dff852bc9dcf7c998b8","tid":434902,"uid":35961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T17:15:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪無左章魚餅啦？<br />\n同埋個牛油帶子點整 好好食</blockquote><br />\n章魚餅應該冇咗啦 早排轉menu<br />\n我好多嘢都冇食過 牛油帶子都係其中一樣<br />\n想知係咩味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋牛油帶子係其中一樣野成日冇貨</blockquote><br />\n牛油帶子個醬係中央廚房果邊整好pack好送去分店，分店班廚房佬都唔會知個醬點調出黎"},{"pid":"d36d03d4eabd99023b884ea66318c1ed67bee7c8","tid":434902,"uid":76883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T20:55:29.000Z","msg":"係咪真係有人order吐司？<br />\n利申 好耐無去過和民，唔知依加呢個甜品仲有無"},{"pid":"eb5788b9e2ce46f425e7344aa5ffeac0a010ff7e","tid":434902,"uid":6573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T21:16:09.000Z","msg":"我今期負loss阿"},{"pid":"0288a4fa03c6e5bc1fddd05ce513fbe6fe034188","tid":434902,"uid":51435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T22:42:53.000Z","msg":"前ft留名"},{"pid":"8529789fca84fa7ccc38bebdc72abd825d6c0eed","tid":434902,"uid":127223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:27:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪真係有人order吐司？<br />\n利申 好耐無去過和民，唔知依加呢個甜品仲有無</blockquote><br />\n吐司都冇咗啦 甜品得返幾款"},{"pid":"5d3ffa96329d6c5dffa6fb8f2556bb2a17ad88e6","tid":434902,"uid":41052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T13:16:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d11a6b05f65d5646da639db1367485c923b0e7","tid":434902,"uid":47747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T18:33:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾錢個鐘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n50<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n返緊和民旗下既一間西餐 43蚊個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a277adab595315de504bac671e65b627f9dc7b","tid":434902,"uid":47926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T19:44:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個海鮮火鍋好食 但好貴 又慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 次次最少等成廿分鐘</blockquote><br />\n講真真係好睇嗰廚房做野快唔快手<br />\n如果執火鍋嗰位快嘅 出餸嗰位唔冧檔 可以快快手出 樓面同事又醒水俾定嗰爐 咁都唔係等好耐嘅</blockquote><br />\n因為要同客人eye level一樣 好多日菜都要咁"},{"pid":"4b4216dc2b9b2a6245f692d1a555b62b83cfac77","tid":434902,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T23:49:12.000Z","msg":"韓式伴飯係咪轉左整法定換左隻辣椒醬？ 之前前隻味燒烤味重d點整？"},{"pid":"de2e788a16bf139eb0d0c0f82f82a0c2423bb5d8","tid":434902,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T01:28:51.000Z","msg":"仲有冇燒魚翅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6b31fbc32fc24dc00ae799f260194d2735ddcb","tid":434902,"uid":92512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T01:30:14.000Z","msg":"點解冇左廣島燒餅嫁屌"},{"pid":"44bd643de2f230201eabed7d0b0d0e5718f17b85","tid":434902,"uid":127223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T03:37:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>韓式伴飯係咪轉左整法定換左隻辣椒醬？ 之前前隻味燒烤味重d點整？</blockquote><br />\n我做嗰間已經冇咗韓式伴飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}